1
00:00:03,169 --> 00:00:03,837
Let's go.

2
00:00:03,837 --> 00:00:04,837
Rematch!

3
00:00:04,938 --> 00:00:07,474
Or should we do a dry run now?

4
00:00:11,244 --> 00:00:12,946
Come on, let's go for a drive.

5
00:00:16,282 --> 00:00:18,251
Hey, wait for me!

6
00:00:19,352 --> 00:00:20,787
Wait up!

7
00:00:21,254 --> 00:00:22,155
Okay, let's take a breather.

8
00:00:22,155 --> 00:00:23,155
Sound good?

9
00:00:26,559 --> 00:00:28,061
It's so beautiful.

10
00:00:31,831 --> 00:00:33,832
Look, it's gorgeous.

11
00:00:33,833 --> 00:00:36,036
What are you taking photos of? Let me see.

12
00:00:38,471 --> 00:00:39,906
What's with this prop camera?

13
00:00:40,106 --> 00:00:41,573
Why is it full of photos of me?

14
00:00:41,574 --> 00:00:42,876
This one is hideous.

15
00:00:43,009 --> 00:00:43,476
You can't delete it.

16
00:00:43,477 --> 00:00:45,779
I have a double chin! No way!

17
00:00:47,514 --> 00:00:48,781
Not this one, please.

18
00:00:48,782 --> 00:00:50,016
Are you guys still filming?

19
00:00:50,683 --> 00:00:51,917
We just wrapped for the day.

20
00:00:51,918 --> 00:00:52,852
Are you on a date?

21
00:00:52,853 --> 00:00:54,386
Can we get a photo of you two?

22
00:00:54,387 --> 00:00:55,387
Sure, come on over.

23
00:00:55,588 --> 00:00:56,556
Oh, we don't want to be in it.

24
00:00:56,557 --> 00:00:57,589
We just want a photo of you two.

25
00:00:57,590 --> 00:00:58,191
You guys pose,

26
00:00:58,192 --> 00:00:59,272
and we'll take the picture.

27
00:01:00,660 --> 00:01:01,660
Okay.

28
00:01:02,595 --> 00:01:04,531
We're huge fans of your ship!

29
00:01:04,864 --> 00:01:06,231
We really hope you end up together.

30
00:01:06,232 --> 00:01:07,232
Good luck!

31
00:01:07,333 --> 00:01:08,334
Thank you. Thanks.

32
00:01:09,035 --> 00:01:10,035
Thanks! Bye!

33
00:01:13,406 --> 00:01:14,873
They think we're actually dating.

34
00:01:14,874 --> 00:01:16,194
Why didn't you set them straight?

35
00:01:16,376 --> 00:01:17,410
They're shippers.

36
00:01:17,710 --> 00:01:18,710
We have to give them what they want.

37
00:01:18,711 --> 00:01:19,831
Let them have their fantasy.

38
00:01:21,948 --> 00:01:23,188
You seem pretty happy about it.

39
00:01:23,750 --> 00:01:24,717
I just think...

40
00:01:24,718 --> 00:01:26,586
Watching them imagine all these things...

41
00:01:27,687 --> 00:01:29,689
I start to wonder, "Is that us?"

42
00:01:30,123 --> 00:01:31,424
And it starts to feel right.

43
00:01:34,427 --> 00:01:36,463
Maybe it's because
it's my first acting gig.

44
00:01:36,930 --> 00:01:38,431
I'm just too deep in character.

45
00:01:39,165 --> 00:01:40,432
But whenever I think about tomorrow,

46
00:01:40,433 --> 00:01:42,034
and how we have to film our breakup,

47
00:01:42,035 --> 00:01:43,103
it actually hurts.

48
00:01:46,172 --> 00:01:47,172
I mean,

49
00:01:47,740 --> 00:01:48,675
when someone has been by your side

50
00:01:48,676 --> 00:01:49,709
for such a long time,

51
00:01:49,976 --> 00:01:51,411
how could you not catch feelings?
